quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  21,102,"∆Āe nanoytaa wuu…óaango magge kam…ďe he…ďe e ndeer ko woŇčkiiji ma…ď…ďe lokaa(woo…óa) ko, ko …ďe duumotoo…ďe."
  21,103,"Suninoytaa…ďe …óen∆īere mawnde nde, Maleykaaji …ďen no ja…ď…ďoo…ďe […ďe mbia:] "Ko ndee woni √Ďalaande mo'on, nden nde laatino…óon ho…óon podee"."
  21,104,"√Ďande Min taggoyta kammu ngun wano taggugol …óerol defte. Ko wano Min pu…ó…óori non ka arannde tagoore Min nduttirta nde, […óum] ko Fodoore e dow amen, pellet, Minen Min laatike golloo…ďe."
  21,105,"GooŇč…óii Min mbinndiino ka Jabuura …ďaawo Alluwal deenangal ngal, pellet, leydi ndin ko jeyaa…ďe Am mo∆ī∆īu…ďe …ďen ndonoyta ndi."
  21,106,"Pellet,no e …óuum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo] jottingol wonan'de yim…ďe rewoo…ďe …ďen."
  21,107,"Min Nuliraani ma si wonaa Yurmeende wonan'de winndire nde."
  21,108,"Maaku: "Anndu ko Wahayinaa e am, wonan'dema Dewetee…óo mon On ko O Dewetee…óo Gooto. Enee, hara onon ko on jebbilii…ďe?"."
  21,109,"Si tawii …ďe mduŇčtiima, maaku: "Mi anndinii on e dow potondiral, pellet, mi anndaa si no …ďadii maa …óum si no wo…ó…ói ko ko poda…óon"."
  21,110,"Pellet, KaŇčko himo Anndi ko fee√Īi ko e konngol ngol, homo Anndi kadi ko cuu…óoton."
  21,111,"Mi anndaa non, mbelejo'o …óuum ko jarrabuyee mo'on, e dakamme haa e dummunne."
  21,112,"Maaku: "Jooma, √Ďaawir Goonga kan ko Joomi amen jurmotoo…óo o woni ballitortee…óo On e dow ko cifoto…óon"."